data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!!  This well maintained 4 bed / 2 bath home with an OFFICE is filled with gorgeous details – crown molding and high ceilings throughout, and natural stone flooring.  A barn door provides style & privacy for the large office with unique ceiling and lots of natural light.  The formal dining has crown molding, wainscoting & beautiful accents.  The kitchen is open to the living room and breakfast area and features stainless appliances, granite countertops, & abundant cabinets.  A focal point of the living room is the wood burning fireplace perfect for cozy winter nights.  The master suite is a secluded retreat with a bay window overlooking the back yard, wood flooring, garden tub, separate shower and a HUGE walk-in closet.  The 3 secondary bedrooms, located on the other side of the home, are all generously sized and have carpet and ceiling fans.  The utility room with a sink, & built-in cabinets also has space for an extra refrigerator/freezer.   Out back you will find an oversized covered porch and a newer shed.  Have a boat or RV?  Paved parking and exterior electrical outlet (behind gate) is already here!  Other features include – sprinkler system, manicured lawn and established landscaping, wood privacy fence, and security system.
